      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software quality assurance procedures consistent with MRL 2 requirements, including version control and documented test suite for the CFD solver.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is used under an ISO 9001-certified QMS. Version control and regression test suite documentation confirm Gradation 2 compliance. No deficiencies identified."
    },
