      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Numerical code verification activities demonstrate solver correctness for incompressible viscous flow at MRL 2 through benchmark test cases.",
      "rationale": "Lid-driven cavity and Poiseuille flow benchmark results show second-order convergence consistent with published norms. Code verification satisfies MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Discretization error estimated via Richardson extrapolation or equivalent; GCI reported for hemolysis index QOI.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the FDA GCBP geometry. GCI for hemolysis index is 4.2% on the medium mesh selected for production runs, within acceptable bounds for MRL 2."
    },
    {
