      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (fluid properties, rotational speed, flow rate) are documented and traceable to the validation dataset.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions are fully documented in the published protocol. Glycerol-water analog fluid properties at 37°C match simulation inputs to within 1.5%. Traceability confirmed."
    },
    {
